    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Casting Divination spells comes so easily to you that it expends only a fraction of your spellcasting efforts. When you cast a Divination spell using a level 2+ spell slot, you regain one expended spell slot. The slot you regain must be of a level lower than the spell you cast and can't be higher than level 5.</p><section id=\"secret-lSc1dDZqiYfzEvzH\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>You can manually regain the expended spell slot or use the <strong>Regain Spell Slot</strong> activity which will prompt you for the slot to restore.</p></section>",
